    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people who\u2019ve had covid-19 to travel under same restrictions as vaccinated",
        "additional_details": "People who have had covid-19 have antibodies, like those who have been vaccinated, and some studies suggest that people who have had it can have even stronger antibodies than those who have been vaccinated.",
        "background": "The Government should apply the same travel rights and restrictions on international travel to those who had covid-19 as apply to those who have been vaccinated, providing they can prove it. This could be done through an antibody test.",
